data.description: This UPDATED Townhome really has it all.  Main Level Living, with a Walk-out basement.   Open-concept living with a Spacious Living Room, vaulted ceilings & morning sunlight streaming through expansive windows.  Enjoy your kitchen w/Brand NEW Stainless appliances, Blue Pearl Granite countertops, breakfast bar & dining area, making it great for entertaining.  Two main level bedrooms, the primary w/ walk through 3/4 bathroom & spacious walk-in closet. The main floor bath was redone to be a  3/4 bath w/ Kohler Luxstone Shower. Maintenance-free deck.  Attached 2 car garage w/ Epoxy flooring & LAUNDRY on Main level! Newer mechanicals downstairs. Finish the basement to your liking!  Much storage and a lower walk out cement patio to enjoy!  HOA managed exterior. Close to shops, a trail system to Bunker Hills regional park & quick access to highways.
